    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend getaways. It runs great, looks sharp, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. I've taken good care of it, and I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how smooth it drives! \u2728",
      "price": 28900.0,
