      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant. This unit retains its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, ensuring a broad powerband and immediate spool. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and the original Torsen limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry consists of the factory double-wishbone setup, providing precise turn-in and lateral stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and new valve stem seals to maintain optimal compression and volumetric efficiency. The chassis is straight with consistent panel gaps, showing only minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver's car. Mechanically sound and ready for the circuit or the collection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
