      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road-wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with supple leather seating that remains supportive and comfortable for long journeys. All power features, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium infotainment system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready; it has been strictly maintained with documented oil changes and a recent full-system inspection. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth, quiet ride that demonstrates its excellent mechanical health. Whether you're commuting or taking a weekend trip, this car provides a dependable and elevated driving experience that feels premium in every way.",
